<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 29 at 10:52PM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Patchy dense fog through the overnight hours...
Patchy fog is expected to continue through the night across
eastern New York and western New England. Visibilities may be
below half a mile at times. Motorists should use caution and allow
extra space between vehicles.</description>
